      "type": "text",
      "text": {
        "content": "<p><em>Britannia's history from pre-Roman times through 145 A.D. (reign of Antoninus Pius). Key events: druidic influence, Roman invasion (43 A.D.), Boudican Uprising, construction of Stonehenge and other ritual henges. Eihort, Byatis, and other Great Old Ones appeared at various points in deep history.</em></p><p><em>Refer to the Britannia & Beyond rulebook for full details.</em></p>",
